title: Russia's Luna-25 probe enters Moon orbit
description: Moscow's first lunar launch since 1976 comes after the European Space Agency announced it would not co-operate with Russia on future missions, over its invasion of Ukraine.

title: Discovering the liquid world of female arousal
description: This summer, columnist Maïa Mazaurette embarks on an adventure like no other as she steers her vessel through the currents of sexuality's diverse fluids.
